Package: ggsunburst
Title: Adjacency diagrams with ggplot2
Description: Tools for extracting data from a tree structure,
    and plot it as adjacency diagrams (sunburst and icicle).
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Didac Santesmasses <didac.santesmasses@crg.eu>
Maintainer: Didac Santesmasses <didac.santesmasses@crg.eu>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2),
    reticulate (>= 1.11.1),
    ggplot2 (>= 2.2.1)
Suggests:
    reshape2 (>= 1.4)
License: GPL-3
SystemRequirements: python, python-os, python-re, python-math,
    python-collections
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
